              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#555555' fontname='Benton Sans Book' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Cancellations spike during the 8:00 AM morning commute (1.32M) and peak again during the 5:00 PM evening rush (1.51M).</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
