              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#555555' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>: Although monthly revenue has fully recovered to roughly $160M in 2026, the platform is still losing an estimated $35M per month to driver idle time (based on $17.60/hour). This points to a major efficiency gap and a clear opportunity to improve profitability through better route-matching and utilization.</run>
